I had to read that sentence about 5 times before it began to make sense,
and I'm still not sure I've understood it, as what you are suggesting seems
quite bizarre. I don't believe I've ever previously met anyone who asks a
question & when he is told how to find the answer, responds indignantly
with "Give me the damn answer! Did I give you permission to treat me as one
of your students?"

>In fact, it's just the kind of position that leads to the reputation for
