You've lost me again, sorry.  Are you referring to your own position, or to
mine?  If the latter, I think you need to learn how to read and understand
email addresses.

>Frankly I'm now not only fed up, but also disgusted at the bright people,
>who were given natural gifts through no effort of their own, who were mostly
